<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20mm;
            background: white;
        }
        .ruler {
            border: 1px solid #333;
            position: relative;
        }
        .horizontal-ruler {
            height: 10mm;
            width: 100mm;
            margin: 10mm 0;
        }
        .vertical-ruler {
            width: 10mm;
            height: 100mm;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 20mm;
        }
        .marker {
            position: absolute;
            background: #333;
        }
        .h-marker {
            width: 1px;
            height: 5mm;
            top: 0;
        }
        .v-marker {
            height: 1px;
            width: 5mm;
            left: 0;
        }
        .scale-info {
            background: #f0f8ff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 1em;
            margin: 1em 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>

    <div class="scale-info">
        <h2>Scale Validation Rulers</h2>
        <p>These rulers help validate that the PDF maintains correct scale and measurements.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Horizontal Scale (100mm)</h2>
    <div class="ruler horizontal-ruler">
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 0mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 10mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 20mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 30mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 40mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 50mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 60mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 70mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 80mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 90mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker h-marker" style="left: 100mm;"></div>
    </div>

    <h2>Vertical Scale (100mm)</h2>
    <div class="ruler vertical-ruler">
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 0mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 10mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 20mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 30mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 40mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 50mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 60mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 70mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 80mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 90mm;"></div>
        <div class="marker v-marker" style="top: 100mm;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="scale-info">
        <h2>Testing Notes</h2>
        <p>Measure the rulers in the generated PDF:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Horizontal ruler should be exactly 100mm wide</li>
            <li>Vertical ruler should be exactly 100mm tall</li>
            <li>Each marker should be 10mm apart</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>